headline: Q4 Earnings Highs And Lows: Envista (NYSE:NVST) Vs The Rest Of The Dental Equipment & Technology Stocks
summary: Quarterly earnings results are a good time to check in on a company’s progress, especially compared to its peers in the same sector. Today we are looking at Envista (NYSE:NVST) and the best and worst performers in the dental equipment & technology industry.
